title: Ep. #73 | Catching Up: Jessi (제시)
description:
The one and only Jessi is in the house today, folks! Find out how she went from a small town choir girl in Jersey to arguably the most well-known contestant on Unpretty Rapstar and the powerhouse solo artist that she is today.
